&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;Let the&amp;nbsp;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);&quot;&gt;quantity of copper added to the alloy be x.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;3 units&amp;nbsp;&amp;rarr; 60&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);&quot;&gt;1 unit&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);&quot;&gt;&amp;rarr; 20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);&quot;&gt;The initial quantity of copper in the alloy = 1&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 20 = 20&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;The initial quantity of gold in the alloy = 2&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 20 = 40&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;(40)/(20 + x) = 1/2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;rArr; x = 80 - 20 = 60 grams.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;color: rgb(30, 43, 51);   user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bolder;  line-height: 20px; user-select: text !important; pointer-events: initial !important;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; The answer is 60 grams.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Calculation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let the number be &amp;#39;x&amp;#39;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;45% of x = 180&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; (45/100)&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; x = 180&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; x = 180&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; (100/45)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; x = 400&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1/8 th of number = (1/8)&amp;nbsp;&amp;times; 400&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; 50&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;there4; The required number is 50&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

